Crédit Agricole Corporate & Investment Bank
                                    






Crédit Agricole Corporate & Investment Bank
Crédit Agricole Corporate & Investment Bank is part of the Crédit Agricole Group.










Crédit Agricole CIB offers its customers a range of products and services in the areas of structured finance, client coverage and international network, debt optimisation and distribution, capital markets and investment banking. 




