        crédit agricole corporate & investment bank
      

CACIB offers its international clients a comprehensive range of products and services structured around six major divisions: Client Coverage & International Network; Global Investment Banking; Structured Finance; Global Markets; Debt Optimisation & Distribution; International Trade & Transaction Banking.












